data.title: Berner, Wiz Khalifa & Problem Show You How to Grind "Night & Day"
data.meta_description: A bonus cut from Berner's latest project Drugstore Cowboy.
data.text:

Berner released the deluxe edition of his latest mixtape Drugstore Cowboy on iTunes today and included on this new version is "Night & Day" featuring Taylor Gang cohort Wiz Khalifa and Compton's own Problem. The record is smooth enough to initiate a laidback smoke session, which is something these three rappers have been known to do on occasion. It's also a song that has a motivational tone to it. After countless days of grinding, Berner is seeing his dreams turn into a reality.

[via HHNM]
